<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="stare-v">stare <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /steə(r)/    美 /ster/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>盯；凝视：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>stare sb up and down
上下打量某人</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s rude to stare.
盯着人看是没有礼貌的。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>stared at</strong> the painting, wondering where she had seen it.
她凝视着这幅画，想知道自己曾在哪里见过它。</p><footer>2009 重庆</footer></div></div>